---
title: "Content pipeline: draft → publish (target / Planned)"
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant Trig as Trigger (cron Mon/Wed/Fri or on-demand)
    participant Gen as Post Generator
    participant SC as Self-correction
    participant Ver as Self-verification
    participant HITL as HITL pause (Inngest)
    participant User as User (Dashboard)
    participant LI as LinkedIn

    Trig->>Gen: generate draft from insight
    Gen->>SC: improve draft (score 0.51 → 0.79)
    SC->>Ver: verify facts
    Ver-->>Ver: VERIFIED / UNVERIFIED / CONTRADICTED
    Ver->>HITL: pause for human review
    HITL->>User: draft waiting in DraftInbox
    User-->>HITL: approve / edit
    HITL->>LI: publish (stub until LinkedIn API)
    LI-->>User: post live
